            <note xml:id="foot.f2">For more on the attitudes to consanguineous marriage around this time, see <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_160.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Anderson 1986</ref> and <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_4520.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Kuper 2002</ref>. See also <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1385.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Child 1862</ref> and <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_16.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Adam 1865</ref>.</note>
